      "comment": "MAJOR FORTE (5) flew the lids from the middle with an impressive turn of foot, going on to clock 22.97 when a 4 length winner over 400m at The Gardens. Was a winner at his only start from this draw. Expected to be right there at the finish again. MISS LOUELLA (1) was unwanted in betting when starting from the same box but ran very well, finishing in the minors over 400m at this track in a Mix 2/3 in 23.06. Worth another try. ZIPPER TRAIN (2) was safely held last time out, finishing fifth at Gosford over 515m behind Great Chat (30.26) in a Grade 4/5. Key runner who gets his chance to atone. HEART DESIRES (7) has top-three claims while fresh from a five months break.",
